                              Install


Just drag Multitudinous V5.0 and MConfigs directroy into the Directory
of your choice, Multitudinous V5.0 and the MConfigs directory MUST be in 
the same Directory, other wise Multitudinous V5.0 won't find the Configs.	

You will also have to copy 4 Fonts into your FONTS: Directory, they are:-

				20001
				gtbmenu
				helvetica
				topaz

If these fonts are not in your Sys:Fonts Directory Multitdinous will alert
you of the fact and quit.

